    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIGGERS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/fe4253f6c23ac23a90df91de0c8315fd.poster.avif?t=1727794812\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/fe4253f6c23ac23a90df91de0c8315fd.webm?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/fe4253f6c23ac23a90df91de0c8315fd.mp4?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Recruit a zany cast of diggers to help you reach the core of the planet in this completely free idle mining game demo!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEMO STORE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/229d198e797472f5c4356e72c6d36e67.poster.avif?t=1727794812\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/229d198e797472f5c4356e72c6d36e67.webm?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/229d198e797472f5c4356e72c6d36e67.mp4?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Earn rubies by playing the demo and spend them in the Demo Shop to unlock new items like character skins in the main Click Click Dig game. The demo also features an entirely new planet not found in the main game, new skins, new tasks, and more! Play the demo and the main Click Click Dig game in order to unlock everything!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POSITION BONUSES!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/d27a1168199e7e01e4a3cfdf3b95c3ba.poster.avif?t=1727794812\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/d27a1168199e7e01e4a3cfdf3b95c3ba.webm?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/d27a1168199e7e01e4a3cfdf3b95c3ba.mp4?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mine strategically! Position characters to take advantage of powerful stat bonuses. Characters have a stat type that gets boosted when they're on a bonus block. They also apply bonuses to different patterns of blocks. Change the layout to boost the stats you want!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SKINS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/bffe7825f9f894d0707455574f1a41dc.poster.avif?t=1727794812\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/bffe7825f9f894d0707455574f1a41dc.webm?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/bffe7825f9f894d0707455574f1a41dc.mp4?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every digger has multiple unlockable skins. Each skin gives an immediate, permanent bonus just for owning it. There are tons to choose from, so pick your favorite and get digging!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MINING!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/442ab321d751cffcef0e8fe96e2c448f.poster.avif?t=1727794812\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/442ab321d751cffcef0e8fe96e2c448f.webm?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168920/extras/442ab321d751cffcef0e8fe96e2c448f.mp4?t=1727794812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every planet has a unique ore to mine. Refine the ore into materials, then use them to craft powerful items that provide stat boosts.<br><br> <strong>And much more:</strong><br>⛏️ complete research for bonuses <br>⛏️ idle and clicker gameplay<br>⛏️ tasks <br>⛏️ incremental progression<br>⛏️ benefactors <br>⛏️ idle progression<br>⛏️ planet shops <br>⛏️ challenge mode <br>⛏️ golden worms <br>⛏️ offline mining modes <br>⛏️ geode prizes <br>⛏️ treasure chests <br>⛏️ big bangs!<br>⛏️ completely free!",
